Package io.honeycomb.beeline.spring.utils

Class MoreTraceFieldConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.honeycomb.beeline.spring.utils.MoreTraceFieldConstants

  • public final class MoreTraceFieldConstants
extends Object
    Class to keep the names of fields not (yet) defined in the Beeline specs or ones that are spring/java-specific. See also TraceFieldConstants for defined ones.
